## Step 3: Apply Visual Design

Read the Design section in [pptx SKILL.md](/mnt/skills/public/pptx/SKILL.md) for full palette and typography options.

### Quick Design Decisions

**Pick a theme that matches the context:**

| Context | Recommended Theme | Feel |
|---------|------------------|------|
| Tech / Startup | Midnight Executive or Ocean Gradient | Modern, bold |
| Finance / Consulting | Charcoal Minimal or Midnight Executive | Authoritative |
| Healthcare / Education | Teal Trust or Sage Calm | Trustworthy |
| Creative / Marketing | Coral Energy or Berry & Cream | Energetic |
| Sustainability / NGO | Forest & Moss or Sage Calm | Organic |

**Layout variety rule — never repeat the same layout twice in a row:**

| Slide Content | Suggested Layout |
|---------------|-----------------|
| Key stat / metric | Giant number callout (60-72pt) + small label |
| Comparison | Two-column split |
| Process / Steps | Numbered horizontal flow |
| List of features/benefits | Icon grid (2×2 or 2×3) |
| Quote / Testimonial | Full-bleed accent color + large italic text |
| Data | Chart with annotation callout |
| Image-heavy | Half-bleed photo + content overlay |

