## Step 4: Generate the File

Use **pptxgenjs** to produce the `.pptx` file. Read [pptxgenjs.md](/mnt/skills/public/pptx/pptxgenjs.md) for the full API reference.

### Quickstart Pattern

```bash
# Install if needed
npm install -g pptxgenjs

# Write and run the generation script
node generate-deck.js
```

### Code Structure

```javascript
const pptx = require('pptxgenjs');
const pres = new pptx();

// 1. Set global theme
pres.layout = 'LAYOUT_WIDE';
pres.theme = { headFontFace: 'Georgia', bodyFontFace: 'Calibri' };

// 2. Define reusable styles
const COLORS = {
  primary: '1E2761',
  secondary: 'CADCFC',
  accent: 'FFFFFF',
  dark: '0D1B4B',
  text: 'F0F4FF'
};

// 3. Add slides
// Title slide
let slide = pres.addSlide();
slide.background = { color: COLORS.primary };
slide.addText('Presentation Title', {
  x: 0.5, y: 2.5, w: 9, h: 1.2,
  fontSize: 44, bold: true, color: COLORS.accent,
  fontFace: 'Georgia'
});

// ... add more slides ...

// 4. Save
pres.writeFile({ fileName: 'output/presentation.pptx' });
```

### Key pptxgenjs Patterns

**Stat Callout Slide:**
```javascript
slide.addText('40%', { x: 2, y: 1.5, w: 6, h: 2, fontSize: 80, bold: true, color: COLORS.accent, align: 'center' });
slide.addText('Year-over-Year Revenue Growth', { x: 1, y: 3.8, w: 8, h: 0.5, fontSize: 18, color: COLORS.secondary, align: 'center' });
```

**Icon Grid (using emoji as placeholder icons):**
```javascript
const items = [
  { icon: '🚀', title: 'Speed', desc: 'Deploy in minutes' },
  { icon: '🔒', title: 'Security', desc: 'Enterprise grade' },
  // ...
];
items.forEach((item, i) => {
  const col = i % 2, row = Math.floor(i / 2);
  const x = 0.5 + col * 4.75, y = 1.5 + row * 2;
  slide.addText(item.icon, { x, y, w: 0.8, h: 0.8, fontSize: 32 });
  slide.addText(item.title, { x: x + 0.9, y, w: 3.5, h: 0.4, fontSize: 16, bold: true, color: COLORS.primary });
  slide.addText(item.desc, { x: x + 0.9, y: y + 0.45, w: 3.5, h: 0.4, fontSize: 13, color: '444444' });
});
```

**Two-Column Layout:**
```javascript
// Left column
slide.addShape(pres.ShapeType.rect, { x: 0, y: 0.9, w: 4.8, h: 6.1, fill: { color: COLORS.primary } });
slide.addText(leftContent, { x: 0.3, y: 1.2, w: 4.2, h: 5.5, fontSize: 14, color: COLORS.accent });
// Right column
slide.addText(rightContent, { x: 5.2, y: 1.2, w: 4.3, h: 5.5, fontSize: 14, color: '333333' });
```

